This meshtastic-arduino_src folder contains Meshtastic protobuf definitions and core protocol files
from https://github.com/meshtastic/Meshtastic-arduino/tree/master/src

IMPORTANT: DO NOT MANUALLY EDIT FILES IN THIS DIRECTORY

- ESP32-specific customizations: lib/meshtastic_customizations/esp32_overrides/
- Critical bug fix patches: lib/meshtastic_customizations/patches/
- Automated update script: lib/meshtastic_customizations/update_scripts/update_meshtastic.py

CURRENT PATCHES APPLIED:
1. mt_protocol.cpp:686 - Rebooted tag return statement fix (prevents crash on GCM reconnection)

To update Meshtastic library:
  cd lib/meshtastic_customizations/update_scripts/
  python3 update_meshtastic.py

This will automatically:
  - Backup current library
  - Download latest upstream code
  - Apply critical bug fix patches
  - Preserve ESP32 customizations
